{"tid":2369432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雞排妹上圍縮水失守32D 自爆入行出寫真虛報尺寸","createTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T08:09:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc8f415968a08962e9acbe8223b9aa11ff5902d","tid":2369432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TTVlOzr46Hh8fP7rhcO_hYR_XNg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2UY2KQ2GGJACPI256KGWN4J56Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTTVlOzr46Hh8fP7rhcO_hYR_XNg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2UY2KQ2GGJACPI256KGWN4J56Q.jpg&h=c7f00f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣性感女星鄭家純（雞排妹）早前進軍商界晉身CEO，創立情趣用品品牌在網上集資火速達標，首波產品飛機杯更秒速售罄，開創副業相當成功。不過她卻因此令原本豐滿的上圍大縮水，雞排妹昨日在社交平台感嘆，最近的忙碌生活帶來了副作用，「創業再斜槓雞排妹，還不小心接案弄企劃。阿純目前忙到變瘦，奶縮水失守D。」有不少粉絲留言卻幽默搞笑「我手小，縮水我還是喜歡」、「沒圖沒真相」、「老婆沒關係，有就好了，老公不會說甚麼的」。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹經常打着E CUP旗號谷胸上陣，不過曾經一次談論到上圍數字的話題時，她就曾自爆剛出道時第一個節目是寫真專題，原本要報內衣尺寸32D，但看前一名模特兒「明明是C卻報D」多報一個尺寸，於是自己就報了E CUP，最後她坦白自己的上圍數字只是32D。她表示其實胸部會隨着體重變化有所增減，自己體重破114磅時確有E CUP，體重最輕時得95磅則縮水到C CUP，最近工作操勞令體重下降，也導致胸部再度縮水。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7tyiSkQwpftYhwFveBH1ebJh3bI=/802x1001/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JH2PXOVFOFHH5B7KXNSK4UB2A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7tyiSkQwpftYhwFveBH1ebJh3bI%3D%2F802x1001%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJH2PXOVFOFHH5B7KXNSK4UB2A4.jpg&h=01ac773b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dshPPhOl2NeyqUSCuwZkRv-Lkwk=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SAK5K2G2GVENZJAQAOPFTUGJVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdshPPhOl2NeyqUSCuwZkRv-Lkwk%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSAK5K2G2GVENZJAQAOPFTUGJVM.jpg&h=3d54a60f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZxroSXn05lB_bbhWW2jUcpcUbMc=/802x883/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ER5H23PQGJCQVLZF4XS5KR5H7Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZxroSXn05lB_bbhWW2jUcpcUbMc%3D%2F802x883%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FER5H23PQGJCQVLZF4XS5KR5H7Q.JPG&h=324d9b71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1858f24ec77283a311b9dacfc03a68efd7f2d1eb","tid":2369432,"uid":17376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"最緊要係個雞屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4638076af2075ab97bc450db1f7a1cf56b97d3e4","tid":2369432,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"我不了....麻麻地雞扒妹 <br />\n無心動嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b661cbeb19370c4bc3c1a85911425dc0a06b0ad","tid":2369432,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"個屎忽無縮水就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4d7ee50edff173a1ff21fffa0b0ed54469da76","tid":2369432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4638076af2075ab97bc450db1f7a1cf56b97d3e4","tid":2369432,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"我不了....麻麻地雞扒妹 <br />\n無心動嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmo